  </p>\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-cream/60\">\n          <strong>p(doom):</strong> 5%. The world would be better if everyone were a bit more tolerant—and more concerned about restoring our beautiful nature.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          <strong>Goals:</strong> Leave an impact on society where everyone benefits—maybe curing cancer, heart disease and dementia would be a good start.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4\">\n        <a\n          href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/jonas-wolber/\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n          rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n          class=\"rounded-full border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:border-teal hover:text-teal dark:border-white/20 dark:text-cream/80 dark:hover:border-mint/50 dark:hover:text-mint\"\n        >\n          LinkedIn\n        </a>\n        <a\n          href=\"https://github.com/Prgrmmrjns\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n          rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n          class=\"rounded-full border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:border-teal hover:text-teal dark:border-white/20 dark:text-cream/80 dark:hover:border-mint/50 dark:hover:text-mint\"\n        >\n          GitHub\n        </a>\n        <a\n          href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Jonas-Wolber-4\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n          rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n          class=\"rounded-full border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:border-teal hover:text-teal dark:border-white/20 dark:text-cream/80 dark:hover:border-mint/50 dark:hover:text-mint\"\n        >\n          ResearchGate\n        </a>\n        <a\n          href=\"https://www.ukaachen.de/kliniken-institute/institut-fuer-digitale-allgemeinmedizin/ueber-uns/team/jonas-wolber/\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n          rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n          class=\"